<bibRefCitation id="EFC7F8E8D11649767D46C518FADB3017" author="Jouault C. &amp; Nel A." box="[1080,1312,1111,1137]" pageId="15" pageNumber="72" pagination="614 - 622" refId="ref15042" refString="Jouault C. &amp; Nel A. 2020. A new species of parasitoid wasps (Hymenoptera: Diapriidae: Belytinae) from Eocene Baltic amber. Palaeoentomology 3 (6): 614 - 622. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / palaeoentomology. 3.6.13" type="journal article" year="2020">Jouault &amp; Nel 2020</bibRefCitation>
) and 
